(559, '\n				Randle prepares to join a crowded frontcourt in L.A.\n				', 'http://www.nba.com/2014/news/07/18/rookie-ladder-after-day-7/index.html?rss=true\n			', 'Neither the departure of Pau Gasol or arrival of Ed Davis were expected to effect Julius Randle and the start of his NBA career that much. Not when Gasol''s departure could be seen coming from months away whether the Lakers added a replacement power forward in the draft or not and Davis signing for the minimum as a free agent indicated the level of belief around the league he is capable of holding down big minutes.', 3, 1405658956, 'Fri, 18 Jul 2014 00:49:16 EDT', 0),
(560, '\n				Wiggins, Cavs hounded by Love trade rumors\n				', 'http://www.nba.com/2014/news/07/17/wiggins-love-trade-rumors.ap/index.html?rss=true\n			', 'Andrew Wiggins came to summer league to get an early education on the NBA game, from playing against better competition to learning about what his new coach with the Cleveland Cavaliers will demand of him as a pro.', 3, 1405661888, 'Fri, 18 Jul 2014 01:38:08 EDT', 0),
(561, '\n				Lakers make winning bid for Boozer\n				', 'http://www.nba.com/2014/news/07/17/lakers-winning-bid-boozer.ap/index.html?rss=true\n			', 'Carlos Boozer is headed to the Lakers'' crowded frontcourt after Los Angeles made the winning bid for the veteran forward waived by the Chicago Bulls via the amnesty clause.', 3, 1405657456, 'Fri, 18 Jul 2014 00:24:16 EDT', 0),
