(565, 'Director of player development Brisebois leaves Canadiens for personal reasons', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726445', '\r\nMONTREAL - Patrice Brisebois is leaving the Montreal Canadiens for personal reasons, a source tells The Canadian Press.\r\n\r\nBrisebois, who has served as director of player development for the past two years, told general manager Marc Bergevin of ...', 4, 1405642501, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 20:15:01 EDT', 0),
(566, 'Official 2014 free agent signings tracker', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=724642', 'NOTE: This is the official free agent signings list as of July 17 at 7:42 PM ET.\r\n\r\nDATE PLAYER 2014-15 TEAM PREVIOUS TEAM\r\n\r\nJULY 17 F Antoine Laganiere Anaheim Anaheim\r\nJULY 17 G John Curry Minnesota Minnesota\r\nJULY 17 F Jacob Josefson New Jerse...', 4, 1405640520, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 19:42:00 EDT', 0),
(567, 'Flames goalie Hiller has appendicitis: report', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726586', 'Calgary Flames goaltender Jonas Hiller needed a minor procedure after having an appendicitis attack working out in Switzerland, the Calgary Sun reported via Twitter. \r\n\r\nFlames beat writer Wes Gilbertson wrote Hiller is "expected to make a speedy ...', 4, 1405637520, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 18:52:00 EDT', 0),
(568, 'Minnesota Wild agree to terms with goalie John Curry on 1-year, 2-way contract', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726443', '\r\nST. PAUL, Minn. - The Minnesota Wild have agreed to terms with goaltender John Curry on a one-year, two-way contract.\r\n\r\nUnder the deal announced Thursday, Curry will be paid his NHL salary only if he is on the NHL roster. If he is sent to the A...', 4, 1405634701, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 18:05:01 EDT', 0),
(569, 'Goaltender Curry signs one-year contract with Wild', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726584', 'Goaltender John Curry and the Minnesota Wild agreed to terms on a one-year, two-way contract, the team announced Thursday. Financial terms were not disclosed.\r\n\r\nCurry, 30, was 7-9-2 with a 2.62 goals-against average, .930 save percentage and one ...', 4, 1405628160, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 16:16:00 EDT', 0),
(570, 'Official 2014 list of available free agents', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=724639', 'NOTE: Below is a list of players, who, effective July 1, became free agents. Players will be removed upon signing with a team.\r\n\r\nANAHEIM DUCKS\r\n\r\nGroup 2 FAs: Andre Petersson, Jakob Silfverberg, Devante Smith-Pelly, Sami Vatanen.\r\n\r\nGroup 3 UFAs:...', 4, 1405627140, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 15:59:00 EDT', 0),
(571, 'Ducks sign forward Laganiere to one-year contract', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726563', 'Left wing Antoine Laganiere signed a one-year contract with the Anaheim Ducks, the team announced Thursday. Financial terms were not disclosed.\r\n\r\nLaganiere, 24, had 10 goals and 18 points in 72 games last season with the Norfolk Admirals of the A...', 4, 1405625640, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 15:34:00 EDT', 0),
(572, 'Devils re-sign Josefson to two-year contract: report', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726581', 'Jacob Josefson has re-signed with the New Jersey Devils, according to NJ.com, which reports the forward received a two-year, $1.6 million contract.\r\n\r\nJosefson, 23, had one goal and three points in 27 games last season.\r\n\r\nThe 20th pick in the 200...', 4, 1405623720, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 15:02:00 EDT', 0),
(573, 'Troy Ward replaces Don Hay as coach of WHL''s Vancouver Giants', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726468', '\r\nVANCOUVER - The Vancouver Giants have hired Troy Ward as their new head coach.\r\n\r\nWard takes over the WHL team after three seasons as coach of the AHL''s Abbotsford Heat, the Calgary Flames'' top minor-league affiliate.\r\n\r\n"It''s an honour," Ward s...', 4, 1405617241, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 13:14:01 EDT', 0),
(574, 'Tim Hunter named coach of Moose Jaw Warriors', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726573', 'Longtime NHL player and assistant Tim Hunter is the new coach of the Moose Jaw Warriors in the Western Hockey League, the team announced Thursday. \r\n\r\nHe replaces Mike Stothers, who coached the Warriors for three seasons before being named coach o...', 4, 1405615500, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 12:45:00 EDT', 0),
(575, 'VerHagen to make spot start in Saturday''s twin bill', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/det/tigers-drew-verhagen-to-make-spot-start-in-saturdays-twin-bill?ymd=20140717&content_id=85014078&vkey=news_det', 'Triple-A Toledo hurler Drew VerHagen will get the assignment for the Tigers'' first game of Saturday''s doubleheader against Cleveland at Comerica Park.', 1, 1405624886, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 15:21:26 EDT\n	', 8),
(576, 'Moya named Eastern League ASG MVP', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/det/tigers-prospect-steven-moya-is-eastern-league-all-star-game-mvp?ymd=20140716&content_id=84970466&vkey=news_det', 'Outfielder Steven Moya, the Tigers'' No. 20 prospect, hit a grand slam and was named MVP of the Eastern League All-Star Game on Wednesday. His blast helped the Western Division defeat the Eastern Division, 5-2.', 1, 1405565501, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 22:51:41 EDT\n	', 8),
(577, 'Setback pushes Dirks'' return to Tigers to unknown date', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/det/setback-pushes-andy-dirks-return-to-unknown-date?ymd=20140716&content_id=84955210&vkey=news_det', 'After a week of game action, Andy Dirks'' comeback from back surgery has hit a snag. The Tigers announced Wednesday that they''ve recalled Dirks from his rehab assignment with Class A Lakeland, and will keep him on the disabled list.', 1, 1405562799, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 22:06:39 EDT\n	', 8),
(578, 'Scherzer earns rare Midsummer Classic win', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/det/tigers-max-scherzer-earns-rare-all-star-game-win?ymd=20140716&content_id=84885138&vkey=news_det', 'Considering Max Scherzer kept calling his regular-season wins an overrated stat last year, it probably shouldn''t be a surprise that he wasn''t making a big deal about earning the victory in the 2014 All-Star Game.', 1, 1405487954, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:19:14 EDT\n	', 8),
(579, 'Cabrera launches first All-Star Game homer', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/det/tigers-miguel-cabrera-launches-first-all-star-game-homer?ymd=20140715&content_id=84842356&vkey=news_det', 'Miguel Cabrera smacked a first-inning homer over the left-field wall Tuesday, and it gave the American League All-Stars a three-run lead in an eventual 5-3 victory. It also put Cabrera on the home run ledger for the first time in nine career appearances in the Midsummer Classic.', 1, 1405489404, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:43:24 EDT\n	', 8),
(580, 'AL-Americans: Jeter, Trout spark victory', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_15_nasmlb_aasmlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=al', 'Mike Trout delivered the go-ahead hit and the game''s first run, winning the All-Star MVP Award, but it was Derek Jeter who stole the show in his final Midsummer Classic. Jeter went 2-for-2 with a run scored to set the tone for the AL, which won home-field advantage in the World Series.', 1, 1405487657, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:14:17 EDT\n	', 8),
(581, 'Tigers still World Series contenders after first half', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/det/detroit-tigers-still-world-series-contenders-after-first-half?ymd=20140715&content_id=84790744&vkey=news_det', 'The Tigers reach the season''s midway point much like they began it, firmly among the World Series contenders, if not among the favorites. How they got there featured a series of unexpected plot twists.', 1, 1405534387, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 14:13:07 EDT\n	', 8),
(582, 'Blue Jays claim southpaw Mills off waivers', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/tor/blue-jays-claim-southpaw-mills-off-waivers?ymd=20140717&content_id=85013366&vkey=news_tor', 'Brad Mills is going back to the organization that drafted and developed him, as the Blue Jays claimed the 29-year-old southpaw off waivers from the Oakland A''s on Thursday,', 1, 1405624531, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 15:15:31 EDT\n	', 5),
(583, 'Blue Jays raise money for 8-year-old''s surgery', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/tor/blue-jays-raise-money-for-8-year-olds-surgery?ymd=20140716&content_id=84939352&vkey=news_tor', 'The Blue Jays Baseball Academy, along with Honda Canada and Whitby Minor Baseball Association, will host a one-day clinic on Sunday at Iroquois Park in Whitby, Ontario, to help raise money for an 8-year-old Blue Jays fan suffering from left spastic hemiplegic cerebral palsy.', 1, 1405605616, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 10:00:16 EDT\n	', 5),
(584, 'Blue Jays aim to finish what they started', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/tor/the-blue-jays-are-in-position-for-their-first-postseason-berth-since-1993?ymd=20140716&content_id=84915316&vkey=news_tor', 'The Blue Jays'' first half was a tale of two seasons all wrapped into 96 games. Toronto began the year with decent enough results but then took the baseball world by storm with an almost unprecedented run in May. It seemed like this might finally be the year the Blue Jays brought their decades-long postseason drought to an end but then all of a sudden everything changed.', 1, 1405529520, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 12:52:00 EDT\n	', 5),
(585, 'Bautista starts as AL clinches home-field advantage', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/tor/jose-bautista-starts-as-al-clinches-home-field-advantage?ymd=20140715&content_id=84835062&vkey=news_tor', 'After an 0-for-2 performance in Tuesday''s All-Star Game, it''s back to work for Jose Bautista as he prepares to lead the Blue Jays in a second-half playoff push.', 1, 1405486383, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 00:53:03 EDT\n	', 5),
(586, 'Wounded Warriors join Brewers on trip', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mil/wounded-warriors-join-milwaukee-brewers-on-trip?ymd=20140717&content_id=85031688&vkey=news_mil', 'Combat veterans Brian Schultz and Shane Kruchten began an all-access experience Thursday during the team''s weekend road trip to Washington, D.C. They are guests of general manager Doug Melvin and his wife, Ellen, who also made a financial donation to the Wounded Warrior Project.', 1, 1405638421, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 19:07:01 EDT', 23),
(587, 'Grieving Segura ready to rejoin Brewers', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140717&content_id=85026528&notebook_id=85026962&vkey=notebook_mil&c_id=mil', 'After enduring personal tragedy, Brewers shortstop Jean Segura has told team officials that he is ready to get back to work. Segura traveled with members of his family on Thursday to Washington D.C., where he will meet the Brewers to begin the second half of the season on Friday, one week after Segura''s 9-month-old son, Janniel, passed away suddenly in the Dominican Republic.', 1, 1405634159, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 17:55:59 EDT', 23),
(588, 'Melvin mum on Trade Deadline plan', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140717&content_id=85026528&notebook_id=85026960&vkey=notebook_mil&c_id=mil', 'If Brewers general manager Doug Melvin plans to be active ahead of the July 31 non-waiver Trade Deadline, he was not willing to share that information publicly on Thursday.', 1, 1405634157, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 17:55:57 EDT', 23),
(589, 'Infielder Falu rejoins Brewers'' organization', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140717&content_id=85026528&notebook_id=85026778&vkey=notebook_mil&c_id=mil', 'Irving Falu''s season took another twist Thursday, when he was re-claimed by the Milwaukee Brewers off waivers. The infielder had been claimed from Milwaukee by the Padres on June 26, and after just 11 games with San Diego, he''ll be headed back to the Brewers'' Triple-A affiliate in Nashville.', 1, 1405634156, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 17:55:56 EDT', 23),
(590, 'Brewers poised for second-half race in NL Central', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mil/milwaukee-brewers-poised-for-second-half-push-in-nl-central?ymd=20140716&content_id=84750066&vkey=news_mil', 'Was it just a temporary swoon, or the start of a Brewers collapse? The second half of the season will tell.', 1, 1405610578, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 11:22:58 EDT', 23),
(591, 'Crew All-Stars confident in second-half turnaround', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140716&content_id=84887248&notebook_id=84887462&vkey=notebook_mil&c_id=mil', 'The Brewers'' All-Stars expressed little doubt Tuesday that the team''s pre-All-Star stumbles were not a sign of trouble ahead.', 1, 1405488929, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:35:29 EDT', 23),
(592, 'Segura on teammates'' minds at All-Star Game', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140716&content_id=84887248&notebook_id=84887706&vkey=notebook_mil&c_id=mil', 'Because the All-Star Game prevented him from attending in person, Brewers third baseman Aramis Ramirez said he sent a surrogate to Monday''s funeral in the Dominican Republic for shortstop Jean Segura''s infant son who passed away suddenly last week.', 1, 1405488928, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:35:28 EDT', 23),
(593, 'All-Star Gomez feels love from Minnesota fans', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140716&content_id=84887248&notebook_id=84887460&vkey=notebook_mil&c_id=mil', 'Twins manager Ron Gardenhire once said of a young Carlos Gomez, "He irritates people, sometimes me." But this week at Target Field, with Gomez back as a National League All-Star, it was all love.', 1, 1405488927, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:35:27 EDT', 23),
